SUMMARY:Paint Your Date! Friday 13th!
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy some artsy fun where you & your partner\, friend\, or spouse can unleash your inner artist & find out how your loved ones see you!\nPaint each other for a night of fun & memory creating. Great for absolute beginners. \nThe results are usually hilarious.\nPotentially terrible art skills are welcome.\nAbsolute beginners who’ve never picked up a paintbrush will have a blast too! \nAn excellent way to create memories that will last a lifetime (with the painted proof to hang on the wall!). A wonderful way to bond & create a memorable experience. All welcome! \nRoom for only 7 pairs/couples. Save your spot ASAP!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/paint-your-date-friday-13th/
