SUMMARY:Raven Gala 2026
DESCRIPTION:It’s that time of year! The Raven Gala 2026 is right around the corner and it is the perfect opportunity to support a theater that brings people together by nurturing young artists\, showcasing local talent\, and keeping the arts vibrant and accessible for our entire community. At a time when arts education and community spaces matter more than ever\, the Raven continues to be a place where imagination thrives and everyone belongs. \nThe Raven’s Gala 2026 is a joyful celebration of the artists\, children\, educators\, and community who bring this theater to life. The evening’s entertainment showcases the heart of the Raven\, with the Raven Players\, whose performances highlight the power of local storytelling and community-driven theater. The celebration continues with Young at Heart Theatre\, the Raven’s resident children’s program\, featuring talented young performers whose creativity\, confidence\, and joy onstage remind us why the arts matter. \nAdding to the magic are the students from St. John’s School\, currently rehearsing Alice in Wonderland which performs on the Raven stage in March. Students from The Healdsburg School will also be performing musical numbers from past and upcoming productions. These young performers are the future of storytelling\, imagination\, and creative expression. \nThe evening builds to a rousing grand finale by nationally known recording artist Pete Stringfellow\, bringing the celebration to an unforgettable close. We even have a special guest\, Assemblyman Chris Rogers\, who will be in attendance! \nFor those seeking the ultimate Raven Gala experience\, a limited number of Platinum Tickets include an exclusive pre-show VIP event at The Taste of Tea featuring Robert Goleman\, whose dazzling performances have been described as “nothing short of astonishing.”\nYour support of the Raven’s Gala directly funds arts education\, youth programming\, and access to the theater for local schools and nonprofit organizations. More than a venue\, the Raven is a gathering place\, and a living reminder that a strong community is defined by its commitment to the arts. We cannot wait to celebrate with you. \nFriday\, March 13th. 7:13 PM; Doors open 6:13 PM.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/raven-gala-2026/
LOCATION:Raven Performing Arts Theater\, 115 North Street\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Art,Other,Recreation,Theater
GEO:38.61252;-122.87053
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Raven Performing Arts Theater 115 North Street Healdsburg CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=115 North Street:geo:-122.87053,38.61252
END:VEVENT
