SUMMARY:Pepper on the Run Band at the Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:(Beatles/Wings tribute!)\nBAND BIO: \nPepper on the Run’ (Bio) \nThe Pepper On The Run band is a tribute to the music of Sir Paul McCartney from The Beatles\, Wings and early solo songs! Pepper On The Run plays all of his greatest music\, while leaving out the ones that are too schmaltzy(No “Silly Love Songs” I “Say Say Say” here). One fan calls them\, “Beatles with balls!” They’re based in the San Francisco Bay Area. \nThe members of Pepper on the Run are Tony Lemieux on lead vocals and guitars\, Peter Lomenzo on bass and vocals\, Ian Luke on drums\, Stu Dahlquist on guitar and vocals and John Snee on keyboards. \nThe Pepper on the Run tribute band’s magical mystery tour is coming to a town near you to take you away!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pepper-on-the-run-band-at-the-penngrove-pub/
LOCATION:Penngrove Pub\, 10005 Main Street\, Penngrove\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
